window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Daniel “Rayid” Tear, having defeated the necromancer of the Dow’Del ruins, travels south. His goal: to rescue Pina, the Druid of Barisel and the love of his friend Tol’geth. Along the way they will encounter remnants of lost civilizations, monstrous creatures from the depths of the under-dark, and radical human-only sentiment slowly growing in the Kingdom of Tor.</p> <p>All the while, in the depths of the Great Cathedral and the heart of Sowers Vale, corruption spreads like a plague. The eyes of the Great Valley’s ruinous minions are firmly fixed on the city. Against such odds, what can one barely competent wizard do?</p>"; 
